OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,F'Friendly and gregarious' is how the
OL,7,Ffamily of a university professor from
OL,8,FNottinghamshire will remember her
OL,9,Fafter she was killed by a careless
OL,10,Fdriver.
OL,12,FNicola Verdon was cycling between the
OL,13,Fvillages of Moorhouse and Ossington in
OL,14,FDecember 2024 when she was hit from
OL,15,Fbehind by a car.
OL,17,FThe 54-year-old was a Professor of
OL,18,FBritish Rural History and President of
OL,19,Fthe British Agricultural History
OL,20,FSociety.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
