OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780913124
OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,FShe worked at Sheffield Hallam
OL,7,FUniversity, following lecturing roles
OL,8,Fin Leicester, Harlaxton College and
OL,9,Fthe University of Sussex.
OL,11,FHer research into agricultural labour
OL,12,Fis described by her colleagues as
OL,13,F'groundbreaking' and she leaves a
OL,14,Flegacy of many early-career
OL,15,Fresearchers whom she mentored to go on
OL,16,Fto successful positions.
OL,18,FHer family have paid tribute to her,
OL,19,Fdescribing her as a 'dedicated sister,
OL,20,Faunt, daughter, partner and friend'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
