OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780913124
OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,FIn a statement released by
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police, it reads:
OL,8,F"Nicola grew up in the countryside of
OL,9,FNottinghamshire ` Norwell, Sutton and
OL,10,FNormanton ` and she loved returning
OL,11,Fthere to stay with her parents, walk
OL,12,Fthe fields and enjoy the pubs, as she
OL,13,Fdid at Christmas 2024.
OL,15,F"Nicola was unpretentious, friendly
OL,16,Fand gregarious, always taking time to
OL,17,Ftalk with anyone about pretty much
OL,18,Fanything.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780913124
OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,F"She was a dedicated sister, aunt,
OL,7,Fdaughter, partner, friend and dog
OL,8,Fwalker, who has left us many joyful
OL,9,Fmemories but has passed from us far
OL,10,Ftoo soon."
OL,12,FPeter Hopkinson, 88, pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fcausing death by careless driving. He
OL,14,Fexplained that his vision had been
OL,15,Fimpaired by the low winter sun and
OL,16,Fthat he had not seen Nicola before
OL,17,Fhitting her.
OL,26,@rD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780913124
OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,FHopkinson, of Moorhouse, appeared at
OL,7,FNottingham Magistrates' Court and was
OL,8,Fgiven an eight-month jail sentence,
OL,9,Fsuspended for two years. He was also
OL,10,Fbanned from driving.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Emma Temple, of
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "This
OL,14,Fwas a tragic and entirely avoidable
OL,15,Fdeath that I hope sends a clear
OL,16,Fwarning to all drivers.
OL,18,F"Low winter sunshine is a known
OL,19,Fhazard, particularly when combined
OL,20,Fwith dirty or icy windscreens.
OL,26,@uD@_OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780913124
OL,3,CFamily remember university professor
OL,4,Ckilled by careless driver
OL,6,F"If drivers cannot see clearly in
OL,7,Ffront of them, they have a clear
OL,8,Fobligation under the Highway Code to
OL,9,Fslow down or stop until it is safe to
OL,10,Fproceed.
OL,12,F"The decision of the driver in this
OL,13,Fcase to carry on regardless led
OL,14,Fdirectly to the death of a remarkable
OL,15,Fand much-loved woman who will be
OL,16,Fsorely missed by all who knew her."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
